1
00:00:09,199 --> 00:00:09,679
Chen Hui!

2
00:00:10,199 --> 00:00:11,439
I've been with you all this time.

3
00:00:11,919 --> 00:00:13,119
Just tell me the truth.

4
00:00:13,439 --> 00:00:14,960
Are you a murderer or not?

5
00:00:15,679 --> 00:00:16,640
A murderer?

6
00:00:17,120 --> 00:00:18,039
Chen Hui is a murderer!

7
00:00:18,199 --> 00:00:19,440
Hurry up and leave!

8
00:00:22,199 --> 00:00:23,199
Chen Hui!

9
00:00:23,559 --> 00:00:24,640
Let me tell you!

10
00:00:24,839 --> 00:00:26,600
If you're a man, get out here!

11
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:28,160
I want to see for myself

12
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:30,480
whether you really deserve my Qibao.

13
00:00:30,480 --> 00:00:31,480
Shut up!

14
00:00:32,399 --> 00:00:32,960
Don't be afraid.

15
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:36,159
A real man

16
00:00:37,039 --> 00:00:38,840
never backs down from a fight.

17
00:00:39,119 --> 00:00:39,960
Listen to me!

18
00:00:40,520 --> 00:00:41,759
If you're a man, come out!

19
00:00:41,759 --> 00:00:43,240
And face me in a fight!

20
00:00:44,679 --> 00:00:45,479
Qibao.

21
00:00:46,280 --> 00:00:47,039
I like you.

22
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:49,119
I don't care who's in your heart now.

23
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:51,880
I'll compete with him fair and square.

24
00:00:52,240 --> 00:00:54,280
I won't let him toy with your feelings again.

25
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:56,920
Let's keep him here for now.

26
00:00:57,719 --> 00:00:59,439
And wait for Captain Chu to back us up.

27
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:00,520
Okay.

28
00:01:01,079 --> 00:01:01,960
Chen Hui!

29
00:01:02,439 --> 00:01:03,759
Still not coming out, huh?

30
00:01:04,079 --> 00:01:05,359
Won't come out? Fine.

31
00:01:05,799 --> 00:01:07,200
Then I'm coming in to find you!

32
00:01:08,599 --> 00:01:09,239
Wait for me!

33
00:01:09,799 --> 00:01:10,400
Chen Hui!

34
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:42,400
Wait.

35
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:43,920
Something feels off.

36
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:51,480
Stop right there!

37
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:53,480
Stop!

38
00:01:56,799 --> 00:01:57,599
Stop!

39
00:02:03,079 --> 00:02:03,640
Over here!

40
00:02:07,719 --> 00:02:08,360
Don't move!

41
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:18,240
Looks like he planned his escape route.

42
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:19,560
Split up and chase!

43
00:02:31,599 --> 00:02:32,319
What's wrong with you?

44
00:02:32,319 --> 00:02:33,039
What are you doing?

45
00:02:33,039 --> 00:02:33,599
I don't know.

46
00:02:33,599 --> 00:02:34,199
Police business.

47
00:02:38,719 --> 00:02:39,240
Chen Hui!

48
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:43,319
Don't move!

49
00:02:45,319 --> 00:02:45,800
Go, now!

50
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:46,599
Move it!

51
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:55,919
Chen Hui!

52
00:02:56,159 --> 00:02:57,400
If you've got guts, don't run!

53
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,360
If you're a real man,

54
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,639
come fight me face to face!

55
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:01,759
He's serious!

56
00:03:01,759 --> 00:03:02,919
Run! Run!

57
00:03:03,599 --> 00:03:04,240
Run!

58
00:03:04,319 --> 00:03:04,840
Chen Hui!

59
00:03:07,719 --> 00:03:08,319
Xiao Jun, get in the car!

60
00:03:08,319 --> 00:03:08,759
Don't move!

61
00:03:09,599 --> 00:03:10,199
Let him go!

62
00:03:10,919 --> 00:03:11,520
Let go!

63
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:20,400
Watch him.

64
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:21,800
Are you hurt?

65
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:22,240
No.

66
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:23,479
Call for backup.

67
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:33,080
Tianfang.

68
00:03:34,919 --> 00:03:35,599
Are you okay?

69
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:36,759
Am I okay?

70
00:03:36,759 --> 00:03:38,759
They almost shot me dead!

71
00:03:38,759 --> 00:03:39,719
Tell me the truth.

72
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,199
Who the hell is Chen Hui?

73
00:03:41,479 --> 00:03:42,319
Knowing too much

74
00:03:42,719 --> 00:03:43,599
won't do you any good.

75
00:03:43,599 --> 00:03:44,439
At a time like this,

76
00:03:44,439 --> 00:03:45,639
how can you still cover for him?

77
00:03:45,639 --> 00:03:46,520
He's a criminal.

78
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,719
And he's got a gun!

79
00:03:47,719 --> 00:03:48,840
Can you wake up?

80
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:49,800
As long as you're safe.

81
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:51,560
Wait...

82
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:55,360
The unattainable is always restless,

83
00:03:55,879 --> 00:03:57,439
the favored take it all for granted.

84
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,000
Hey, wait.

85
00:04:00,479 --> 00:04:01,319
Qibao!

86
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,520
Wait for me!

87
00:04:09,039 --> 00:04:09,479
Captain Chu.

88
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,199
He must've run this way.

89
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,360
They went inside.

90
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:25,959
Qin Mo.

91
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:28,120
Before you can stop a crime,

92
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,639
you have to stay alive.

93
00:04:31,199 --> 00:04:33,079
But the man who killed my dad is in there!

94
00:04:35,399 --> 00:04:35,959
Qin Mo.

95
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:39,079
Before, we didn't know who the suspect was.

96
00:04:39,439 --> 00:04:40,319
Now we're sure.

97
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,959
Chen Hui is Chen Dahui.

98
00:04:41,959 --> 00:04:43,120
Per the recusal rule,

99
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,120
you have to step off the case.

100
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,240
But we're about to catch him!

101
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,600
But once you're involved,

102
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,639
all the evidence could potentially

103
00:04:52,639 --> 00:04:53,519
become inadmissible.

104
00:04:54,879 --> 00:04:55,639
You have to withdraw.

105
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:58,439
Backup officers are on their way.

106
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,079
They'll take over from you.

107
00:05:09,879 --> 00:05:10,800
Two hundred thousand,

108
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,480
just to get a bag back.

109
00:05:12,839 --> 00:05:13,720
But what can ever

110
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,319
win back Qiqi's heart?

111
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:24,000
I don't like it when Boss Bai controls me.

112
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:27,040
When she does, she's like a tyrant.

113
00:05:27,399 --> 00:05:28,639
Everything has to be her way.

114
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,800
But I'm also afraid she'll ignore me,

115
00:05:31,399 --> 00:05:32,519
afraid she doesn't love me.

116
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:35,399
This conflict has been tormenting me.

117
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,120
I met a man,

118
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,439
and he said,

119
00:05:38,639 --> 00:05:40,079
if a person isn't seen,

120
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:41,439
they're no different

121
00:05:41,839 --> 00:05:42,839
from being dead.

122
00:05:43,759 --> 00:05:45,560
The reason I act out with Boss Bai,

123
00:05:45,839 --> 00:05:46,519
all the drama,

124
00:05:47,399 --> 00:05:48,839
is because I want her to see me.

125
00:05:58,199 --> 00:05:58,680
Hello?

126
00:05:59,079 --> 00:06:00,240
Got the money ready?

127
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,480
You con artist!

128
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,279
My daughter was never in your hands!

129
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:04,920
Two hundred thousand wasn't enough for you?

130
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,079
You dare call me again?

131
00:06:06,079 --> 00:06:07,160
Go to hell!

132
00:06:07,399 --> 00:06:09,160
Your daughter may be safe,

133
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:11,000
but I still have something of hers.

134
00:06:22,279 --> 00:06:22,600
You.

135
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:23,879
Who are you?

136
00:06:24,079 --> 00:06:25,279
What have you done to my daughter?

137
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,959
I love your daughter very much.

138
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:28,439
She's right here beside me.

139
00:06:28,439 --> 00:06:30,240
I know everything about you.

140
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,519
Don't try anything funny.

141
00:06:31,519 --> 00:06:33,079
Or I'll take all of your daughter's

142
00:06:33,079 --> 00:06:35,240
private secrets and leak them all.

143
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:36,439
Don't.

144
00:06:36,759 --> 00:06:37,319
Stay calm.

145
00:06:37,879 --> 00:06:38,360
Please don't.

146
00:06:40,079 --> 00:06:41,720
Next time, either bring money,

147
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:44,079
or bring Wang Kechen's inheritance.

148
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:07,480
Reporting in.

149
00:07:10,639 --> 00:07:11,079
Chief.

150
00:07:12,079 --> 00:07:12,439
Captain.

151
00:07:12,439 --> 00:07:13,439
We've already searched this area.

152
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:14,360
Nothing was found.

153
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,600
Expand the search radius.

154
00:07:15,839 --> 00:07:16,639
Form a dragnet and advance.

155
00:07:16,639 --> 00:07:17,879
Focus on checking footprints.

156
00:07:17,879 --> 00:07:19,319
Signal immediately if anything's off.

157
00:07:19,319 --> 00:07:20,639
We can't let the fugitives slip away.

158
00:07:21,079 --> 00:07:21,519
Yes, sir.

159
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,279
Sun Bo.

160
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,720
Make sure to check

161
00:07:23,879 --> 00:07:24,959
places easy to hide in.

162
00:07:25,199 --> 00:07:26,480
Abandoned houses, basements.

163
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:28,240
Understood.

164
00:07:29,519 --> 00:07:30,360
Stay safe.

165
00:07:33,639 --> 00:07:34,360
Qin Mo,

166
00:07:34,879 --> 00:07:35,920
don't be too anxious.

167
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:38,079
Recusal isn't about distrust.

168
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,800
It's the firmest safeguard

169
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:41,160
of procedural justice.

170
00:07:41,959 --> 00:07:42,879
Your stepping back for now

171
00:07:43,279 --> 00:07:43,879
is to help

172
00:07:44,199 --> 00:07:46,199
the truth better come to light.

173
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:47,759
Don't worry, Chief.

174
00:07:48,519 --> 00:07:50,040
I'll choose another way

175
00:07:50,279 --> 00:07:51,079
to keep fighting.

176
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:52,360
Good.

177
00:07:58,920 --> 00:07:59,360
Are you okay?

178
00:08:01,079 --> 00:08:01,560
I'm sorry.

179
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,519
I just can't accept it.

180
00:08:05,079 --> 00:08:06,079
A lot of the time,

181
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,079
it's just like playing chess.

182
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:09,680
Before you've won,

183
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,079
we all have to be patient.

184
00:08:11,879 --> 00:08:13,000
If you were Chen Hui,

185
00:08:13,439 --> 00:08:14,800
what would you do next?

186
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,839
I don't think he'll stop.

187
00:08:20,199 --> 00:08:21,160
No matter where he is,

188
00:08:21,759 --> 00:08:22,959
we will find him.

189
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:24,959
Come on.

190
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:26,079
I'll take you back.

191
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,159
We've been running all night.

192
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,240
I'm exhausted.

193
00:08:34,759 --> 00:08:35,759
This place is good.

194
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,279
No one should come here.

195
00:08:37,879 --> 00:08:38,480
Xiao Jun.

196
00:08:39,399 --> 00:08:41,000
With a murder on our hands, there's no going back.

197
00:08:41,279 --> 00:08:42,440
I've dragged you into this.

198
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:43,480
Brother Hui.

199
00:08:44,039 --> 00:08:46,120
My old man always called me a born bad seed.

200
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,919
I just take down whoever crosses me.

201
00:08:48,159 --> 00:08:49,279
We're cut from the same cloth.

202
00:08:49,279 --> 00:08:50,879
From now on, we live it up while we can.

203
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,799
The first piece isn't even on the board.

204
00:08:53,679 --> 00:08:54,720
It's way too early to call the game.

205
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:06,600
Hello.

206
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:08,000
Hello?

207
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,240
Are you ready?

208
00:09:10,879 --> 00:09:11,919
It's time we met.

209
00:09:22,879 --> 00:09:23,480
Boss.

210
00:09:24,919 --> 00:09:25,759
Are you heading out?

211
00:09:26,799 --> 00:09:28,080
I'd like to treat you and Qibao

212
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:28,879
to a meal,

213
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:30,159
to celebrate

214
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:31,759
our great hero Yu Tianfang's

215
00:09:31,759 --> 00:09:33,440
highly successful rescue mission.

216
00:09:34,279 --> 00:09:35,080
Do you have time?

217
00:09:35,759 --> 00:09:36,399
Yu Tianfang,

218
00:09:37,159 --> 00:09:37,720
let me ask you.

219
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,440
If a man deceived

220
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:41,120
a woman's heart and body,

221
00:09:41,399 --> 00:09:42,480
and then abandoned her,

222
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:43,919
what should this woman

223
00:09:43,919 --> 00:09:44,960
do

224
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:47,120
to punish that man?

225
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:48,480
Boss,

226
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:51,000
I... I'm not that kind of man.

227
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,440
A guy like me,

228
00:09:52,799 --> 00:09:55,240
a loyal and devoted good man,

229
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:57,000
compared to those scumbags out there,

230
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:59,279
it's the difference between a saint and a wild boar.

231
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,320
I'm not talking about you.

232
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:01,759
Just tell me,

233
00:10:02,039 --> 00:10:03,600
how do I get back at this scumbag?

234
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:05,720
Well, with a scumbag,

235
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,559
if it's just a romantic dispute,

236
00:10:07,799 --> 00:10:09,519
with no physical harm

237
00:10:09,519 --> 00:10:11,240
or financial disputes involved,

238
00:10:12,039 --> 00:10:12,720
then I'm afraid

239
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,440
the law can't do anything either.

240
00:10:17,279 --> 00:10:19,080
For these so-called scumbags,

241
00:10:19,559 --> 00:10:21,440
basically, all you've got is moral judgment.

242
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,240
Boss,

243
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:23,639
what's wrong?

244
00:10:25,159 --> 00:10:26,000
It's unfair.

245
00:10:26,879 --> 00:10:27,879
This is unfair.

246
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,320
Good people

247
00:10:30,679 --> 00:10:32,080
have their ways,

248
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:34,039
and bad people have theirs.

249
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:35,559
Tell me,

250
00:10:35,559 --> 00:10:36,799
did somebody mess with you?

251
00:10:36,799 --> 00:10:38,080
I'll go find some thugs right now

252
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:39,080
to teach him a lesson.

253
00:10:40,759 --> 00:10:42,080
I... I'm out of water.

254
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,159
Go get me a glass of water.

255
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:44,480
You got it.

256
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:57,559
Here's your water.

257
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,440
Where's the boss?

258
00:11:03,279 --> 00:11:04,720
Don't tell me

259
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:08,360
she went off to tear that scumbag apart?

260
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:10,600
Oh no.

261
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:13,080
Boss Bai!

262
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:14,320
Boss Bai!

263
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:16,440
To the abandoned building east of the city, hurry!
